Interface WorkflowItem

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    Activity<ConfigurationType>, ActivityInputPort, ActivityOutputPort, ActivityPort, AsynchronousActivity<ConfigurationType>, Condition, Configurable<ConfigurationType>, Dataflow, DataflowInputPort, DataflowOutputPort, DataflowPort, Datalink, DispatchLayer<ConfigurationType>, DispatchStack, EventForwardingOutputPort, EventHandlingInputPort, FilteringInputPort, InputPort, IterationStrategy, IterationStrategyNode, IterationStrategyStack, Merge, MergeInputPort, MergeOutputPort, MergePort, MonitorableAsynchronousActivity<ConfigType>, NamedWorkflowEntity, OutputPort, Port, Processor, ProcessorInputPort, ProcessorOutputPort, ProcessorPort, PropertyContributingDispatchLayer<ConfigType>, SupersededActivity<ConfigurationType>, TokenProcessingEntity
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractActivity, AbstractAsynchronousActivity, AbstractDispatchLayer, AbstractErrorHandlerLayer, AbstractEventHandlingInputPort, AbstractFilteringInputPort, AbstractIterationStrategyNode, AbstractOutputPort, AbstractPort, ActivityInputPortImpl, ActivityOutputPortImpl, BasicEventForwardingOutputPort, CompletionHandlingAbstractIterationStrategyNode, CrossProduct, DataflowActivity, DataflowImpl, DataflowInputPortImpl, DisabledActivity, DispatchStackImpl, DispatchStackImpl.TopLayer, DotProduct, ErrorBounce, Failover, IntermediateProvenance, Invoke, IterationStrategyImpl, IterationStrategyImpl.TerminalNodeImpl, IterationStrategyStackImpl, Loop, NamedInputPortNode, NonExecutableActivity, Parallelize, PrefixDotProduct, ProcessorImpl, Retry, Stop, StringConstantActivity, TerminalNode, UnrecognizedActivity

    public interface WorkflowItem
    An item that forms a structural part of a Workflow. Workflow item are Dataflow, its Processor and Port s, and other deeper structural parts like DispatchStack and IterationStrategy.

    Stian Soiland-Reyes
